---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Contacto | Reformas en Valencia, San Diego, Carabobo y Caracas" 
  description="Solicita tu consulta gratuita para reformas en Valencia, San Diego, Carabobo y Caracas. Presupuesto sin compromiso." 
  activePage="contacto"
>
  <header class="page-hero">
    <div class="hero-bg" style="background-image: url('/images/integrales-800.webp')"></div>
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <span class="hero-tag">Hablemos</span>
      <h1 class="page-title">Contacta con <span class="gold">Nosotros</span></h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">Respuesta garantizada en menos de 2 horas hábiles. Atención en Carabobo y Caracas.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container contact-full-grid">
      <div class="contact-info-panel">
        <h2 class="section-title">Información de Contacto</h2>
        <p>Estamos disponibles para atender tu proyecto de reforma. Escríbenos o llámanos directamente. Cubrimos Valencia, San Diego, todo Carabobo y el área metropolitana de Caracas.</p>
        
        <div class="contact-detail">
          <h4>📍 Cobertura</h4>
          <p>Valencia, San Diego, Carabobo y Caracas</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-detail">
          <h4>📞 Teléfono / WhatsApp</h4>
          <p><a href="https://wa.me/584227997043" class="gold-link">+58 422 799 7043</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-detail">
          <h4>⏰ Horario de Atención</h4>
          <p>Lunes a Viernes: 8:00 AM - 6:00 PM</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <form class="contact-form-large" action="https://formsubmit.co/contacto@reformat-venezuela.online" method="POST">
        <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Nueva consulta desde página de contacto">
        <input type="hidden" name="_captcha" value="false">
        <input type="text" name="_honey" style="display:none" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off">
        
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="nombre-c">Nombre completo</label>
            <input type="text" id="nombre-c" name="nombre" required placeholder="Tu nombre" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="telefono-c">Teléfono</label>
            <input type="tel" id="telefono-c" name="telefono" required placeholder="04XX XXX XXXX" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email-c">Correo electrónico</label>
          <input type="email" id="email-c" name="email" required placeholder="correo@ejemplo.com" />
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="proyecto-c">Tipo de proyecto</label>
          <select id="proyecto-c" name="proyecto" required>
            <option value="" disabled selected>Selecciona una opción</option>
            <option value="cocina">Reforma de Cocina</option>
            <option value="bano">Reforma de Baño</option>
            <option value="integral">Reforma Integral</option>
            <option value="electricidad">Electricidad</option>
            <option value="fontaneria">Fontanería</option>
            <option value="otro">Otro</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="mensaje-c">Cuéntanos los detalles</label>
          <textarea id="mensaje-c" name="mensaje" rows="5" required placeholder="Describe brevemente qué necesitas reformar y tu ubicación..."></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn-premium btn-primary-premium full-width">
          <span class="btn-content">Enviar Consulta</span>
          <span class="btn-border"></span>
          <span class="btn-shine"></span>
          <span class="btn-arrow">→</span>
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero { position: relative; min-height: 60vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; color: var(--white); overflow: hidden; padding: 120px 20px 60px; }
  .hero-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; background-size: cover; background-position: center; z-index: 1; }
  .hero-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.5), rgba(0,0,0,0.7)); z-index: 2; }
  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 3; max-width: 800px; }
  .hero-tag { display: block; color: var(--gold); font-size: 0.9rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-weight: 600; }
  .page-title { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem); font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .page-subtitle { font-size: 1.2rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); }
  
  .contact-full-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr; gap: 60px; align-items: start; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 20px; }
  .contact-info-panel h2 { margin-bottom: 25px; }
  .contact-detail { margin-bottom: 30px; padding-bottom: 30px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
  .contact-detail:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .contact-detail h4 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--text); }
  .contact-detail p { color: var(--gray-text); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  .gold-link { color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; transition: 0.3s; }
  .gold-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  
  .contact-form-large { background: var(--white); padding: 40px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
  .form-group { margin-bottom: 25px; }
  .form-group label { display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .contact-form-large input, .contact-form-large select, .contact-form-large textarea { width: 100%; padding: 16px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1rem; background: #fafafa; transition: 0.3s; }
  .contact-form-large input:focus, .contact-form-large select:focus, .contact-form-large textarea:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--gold); background: #fff; }
  .form-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }
  
  .btn-premium { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 10px; padding: 18px 35px; background: var(--gold); color: var(--bg); font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem; text-decoration: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .btn-border { position: absolute; inset: 0; border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); border-radius: inherit; }
  .btn-shine { position: absolute; top: 0; left: -100%; width: 50%; height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.4), transparent); transition: 0.5s; }
  .btn-premium:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.4); }
  .btn-premium:hover .btn-shine { left: 150%; }
  .full-width { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
  
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .contact-full-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .contact-info-panel { order: 2; }
    .contact-form-large { order: 1; padding: 25px; }
    .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>